qDef.qDef:
Interval([App Reload CPU Time (ms)]/86400000,'hh:mm:ss')
//Time([App Reload CPU Time (ms)]/86400000,'hh:mm:ss')

qStringExpression.qExpr:
='Thresholds >> '
& 'App Base RAM (MB): ' & If(GetPossibleCount(AppRAMSizeQuota)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',If(AppRAMSizeQuota='Unlimited',AppRAMSizeQuota,Num(AppRAMSizeThreshold/1048576,'#,##0'))) & '; '
& 'Peak Reload RAM (MB): ' & Num((AppRAMPeakReloadSizeThreshold/1024/1024),'#,##0')
& '; Total Records: ' & If(GetPossibleCount(AppRecordCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',num(AppRecordCountThreshold,'#,##0'))
&'; Total Fields: ' & If(GetPossibleCount(NoOfFields)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',num(NoOfFields,'#,##0'))
&'; Reload CPU Time (minutes): ' & If(GetPossibleCount(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',num(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold/60000,'#,##0'))

='Thresholds >> Record Count: ' & If(GetPossibleCount(FieldValueCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',num(FieldValueCountThreshold,'#,##0')) & '; Field Cardinality: '  & If(GetPossibleCount(FieldCardinalityThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',num(FieldCardinalityThreshold,'#,##0'))

extensionMeta.name: Layout container
extensionMeta.description: The layout container object has a canvas that can hold multiple objects. In this container you can freely move objects around, as well as position the objects on top of each other or overlapping.
extensionMeta.author: QlikTech International AB

bundle.name: Qlik Dashboard bundle
bundle.description:
This is a set of supported objects that will facilitate dashboard creation in Qlik Sense. These can be used in addition to the objects found under "Charts".

For limitations and support conditions, see the documentation.
